<h2>Add Energy Listing ⚡</h2>

<form action="/add-energy" method="POST">

  Energy Amount (kWh):
  <input type="number" name="energyAmount" required><br><br>

Price per kWh:
<input type="number" name="price" step="1" required><br><br>

  Location:
  <input type="text" name="location" required><br><br>

  Time:
  <input type="text" name="time" placeholder="e.g. Evening" required><br><br>

  <button type="submit">Add Listing</button>

</form>

<h3>AI Pricing Insights 🤖</h3>

<p>
Predicted Demand at <%= selectedTime.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + selectedTime.slice(1) %>:
<strong><%= predictedDemand.toFixed(2) %> kWh 🌆</strong>
</p>

<p>
Recommended Price: ₹<%= recommendedPrice %> / kWh ⚡
</p>
